{"tid":1454911,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"仲叫人走??? 今日係戰意最高既時候","createTime":"2019-08-12T08:28:39.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-12T11:25:02.000Z","uid":97330,"like":14,"dislike":23,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"6d46449b5f29060dadaf4c7dcda32dba20f2cb2d","tid":1454911,"uid":97330,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T08:28:39.000Z","msg":"我唔知你地班冷氣軍師點諗<br />\n成日be water be water<br />\n你be water到底有無起到啲咩效果?<br />\n71攻入立法會, 再be water<br />\n但今日真係有做過啲有威脅性既野?<br />\nbe water係岩, 但未做到野之前be water<br />\n只係弱水<br />\n水係流動既時候有雷霆一擊, 依家都未出現<br />\n<br />\n等前線決定啦"},{"pid":"be607bc2747d680721e8d4526c00d00dfedbd3be","tid":1454911,"uid":97330,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T08:29:42.000Z","msg":"推<br />\n係走都去埋T2先"},{"pid":"a8c9dd473f26eadf072443e739b3c3f9cb831879","tid":1454911,"uid":183752,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T08:30:35.000Z","msg":"你講野 風格好似鬼"},{"pid":"fa13982c6aa1d1da5d15b87592994ed4a185d88e","tid":1454911,"uid":165246,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T08:31:58.000Z","msg":"721 811<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">今日所有航班已取消!<br />\n機場圍捕無路走！<br />\n所有手足請即散<br />\n記得係一齊散<br />\n唔好落單！<br />\n擇日再戰<br />\n切實執行不被捕原則！<br />\n仲有咩好留呀 叫你留個d 自己諗下係咪鬼啦</span></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ngYyt3j.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FngYyt3j.png&h=916dd304&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/GSMoRgG.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FGSMoRgG.png&h=734c1f44&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/UYUBrP8.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FUYUBrP8.png&h=f9aef586&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"73f6d2ad55d0153e7f4cbae6c4acc60d0df95abc","tid":1454911,"uid":97330,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"a8c9dd473f26eadf072443e739b3c3f9cb831879","tid":145